com.fasterxml.clustermate.api.msg

Class ListItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fasterxml.clustermate.api.msg.ExtensibleType
      • com.fasterxml.clustermate.api.msg.ListItem

  • public class ListItem
extends ExtensibleType
    Full result entry contained in ExtensibleType (as an alternative to ids, StorableKey).

    Note that since this extends ExtensibleType, extension by adding new entries should be relatively safe, even if old(er) clients; but caller would do well to check if unrecognized properties were found.
